alluxio.client.lineage

Class LineageMasterClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.AbstractClient
      • alluxio.AbstractMasterClient
        • alluxio.client.lineage.LineageMasterClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Client, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @ThreadSafe
public final class LineageMasterClient
extends AbstractMasterClient
    A wrapper for the thrift client to interact with the lineage master, used by alluxio clients. Since thrift clients are not thread safe, this class is a wrapper to provide thread safety, and to provide retries.
